      • equalsIgnoringSuffix

        public boolean equalsIgnoringSuffix(VersionedPackageName other)
        Compare two package name/version pairs for equality, ignoring the suffix part of the version number. For example (http://package-one/, 2.1-alpha) compares equal to (http://package-one/, 2.1-beta)
        Parameters:
        other - the other name/version pair
        Returns:
        true if the values are equal in all respects other than the alphanumeric suffix of the version number.
